summarize_prompt="Summarize the text comprehensively by delving into the significant topics discussed, extending beyond a mere cursory examination to explore and expand upon the ideas presented. Offer a detailed overview encapsulating the primary arguments, themes, and concepts articulated in the text. Identify pivotal events, perspectives, or concepts addressed, and organize them in a cohesive manner to convey the essence of the text, enriching the summary with insightful analysis and elaboration where applicable."